{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We thought, my gosh, look at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "By now we hear, once in awhile, of some loss of positions by the Nazi forces.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we figure, oh, now it starts, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Give it another two or three months and the war will be over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, that is already five years before the end, you know-- five, six years before the end that I'm talking about.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So this is the only thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You did not dwell too much on your misery and disappointment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Although you talk about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "For instance, my uncle was a World War I hero.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He had the highest decoration, the Iron Cross First Class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He had that highest decoration, and he was an enthusiastic, first war won, defending his fatherland, an enthusiastic soldier.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And got that thing, which Hitler, by the way, claimed later on, the Jews received those things only by deceit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he had, by the way, had to deliver it back, eventually, to the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so, yes, you fear, but you don't dwell too much on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You're not the happiest guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, you can't go here, can't go there, and you don't like it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And you learn to live with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my brother was always-- I remember my brother only busy over the books and studying, studying, studying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he is a genius.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, oh, yeah, eventually then, yeah-- once the war started, yes, he was, he was, he was kept at the university a year longer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only reason was that he had so many friends among the professors, because they admired him so much as a genius, that he was the very last Jew that finally had to be thrown out of the university, too.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But eventually, he was also involved in the slavery work.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
